thread.title: Wally Ortiz

author: Wally Ortiz
title: Wally Ortiz
text:
I am writing this letter as a humble note of appreciation for the outstanding class that Anajet provided.
I took a trip from illinos to california to take their free class. For me it was worth the trip. I learned a lot but i still need to learn more. Hopefully ill take another trip next year to take this class again. Thank you Anajet and also thank you Shawn Trender for all your help.. You always answered any questions i had and if you couldn't you always directed me to the right person. Again thank you so much.
